messages.message: Has anyone run into this Banyan issue when trying to log in? I'm working out of the Menlo Park office (and connected to our office WiFi). The links go to JIRA which require me to log in first.
In the Banyan app, does it say "Disconnected"? I got this message and then hit the power button in Banyan to reconnect and login worked

You can set a default service tunnel so it'll auto-connect as well moving forward! https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/IT/pages/2196275239/Banyan+Setup+Login+Notes+Help#Setting-your-Default-Service-Tunnel
